      "content": "a quiet life doesn't sound like anything at all. it just sounds like existing without any purpose. it's like being a ghost in my own skin. if the music is gone, if the thing that made me *me* is just dead, what am i even doing here? hanging on to a body that feels like a costume for someone who isn't there anymore. it feels heavy. just a heavy, useless weight.",
